<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Halo</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>My sadness is gone.<br>
Replaced by anger.<br>
My regret is gone.<br>
Replaced by hate.<br>
My longing is gone.<br>
Replaced by darkness.<br>
My future is gone.<br>
Replaced by fate.<br>
<br>
Along these thoughts alight<br>
I have seen you in the dark of night.<br>
Coming to me when I know thee not.<br>
As I have seen you once before<br>
Grow with light<br>
Fall to darkness rot.<br>
Fading to dust around the mind<br>
Swept away by the god of kind.<br>
Look upon the mirror of mine<br>
Break it and do what thine<br>
Thinks will help thee <br>
Stop your crying.<br>
<br>
Fought so long to see myself<br>
Walk along the golden stones<br>
Of heaven itself,<br>
Instead cast down upon the moans<br>
Of the damned, underneath<br>
The unholy earth that groans.<br>
<br>
Whispers in the mist<br>
Of time’s early mourning<br>
See what you have missed<br>
When you see what you have been ignoring.<br>
Blood forming upon your halo<br>
From all the hearts you bleed.<br>
Stay low, young one, stay low,<br>
And wipe this blood of mine<br>
From your holy halo.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
